A note about xcmsSet objects though: you are using an outdated xcmsSet class; it is strongly suggested to change from the old xcms user interface functions (xcmsSet and alike) to the new functions that make use of the MSnbase package to represent the mass spec data [1].

Best wishes,

Laurent

